items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [exa (zap-zsh) (⭐20)](https://github.com/zap-zsh/exa) - Overrides common commands to use exa instead.
*   [exa-ls (zpm-zsh) (⭐100)](https://github.com/zpm-zsh/ls) - Zsh plugin for ls.
*   [eza (twopizza9621536) (⭐5)](https://github.com/twopizza9621536/zsh-eza) - Replaces `ls` with [eza-community/eza (⭐16k)](https://github.com/eza-community/eza).
*   [no-ps2 (⭐23)](https://github.com/romkatv/zsh-no-ps2) - When this plugin is used, Enter inserts a newline if the typed command is incomplete. No PS2!
*   [run-scripts (⭐5)](https://github.com/Aireck2/zsh-run-scripts) - Runs scripts from `package.json`.

### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [ludvig (⭐0)](https://github.com/daviludvig/ludvig-theme-zsh) - Minimalist. Includes decorators for `git` status, current directory, current time and the last command's exit status.
items.content_html:
Plugins / superconsole - Windows-only

  • exa (zap-zsh) (⭐20) - Overrides common commands to use exa instead.
  • exa-ls (zpm-zsh) (⭐100) - Zsh plugin for ls.
  • eza (twopizza9621536) (⭐5) - Replaces ls with eza-community/eza (⭐16k).
  • no-ps2 (⭐23) - When this plugin is used, Enter inserts a newline if the typed command is incomplete. No PS2!
  • run-scripts (⭐5) - Runs scripts from package.json.

Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • ludvig (⭐0) - Minimalist. Includes decorators for git status, current directory, current time and the last command's exit status.
